# Dramatis Personae

ALICE — The only defined character

# Error Recovery Tests

### SCENE 1

// Unknown character (not in dramatis personae)
UNKNOWN
This character was never declared.

// Orphaned dialogue (text without a character name)
This text just appears without a character speaking it.

ALICE
This is valid dialogue from Alice.

// Another orphan line
More orphaned text that belongs to nobody.

// Missing SONG END
SONG 1: The Unfinished Song

ALICE
  This song never ends,
  it goes on and on my friends.

// No SONG END marker here — the song is unclosed.

### SCENE 2

ALICE
Back to normal dialogue after the unclosed song.

